room_title: Escape room "Ivan’s Lair (Nightmare Part 2)" by Legends of Xscape in West Palm Beach
room_address: 324 Datura St, Suite 101, West Palm Beach, FL 33401
room_description: Unfortunately you were not able to find Ivan’s mask  and save the town. Your goal now is- save yourself! You are locked in the lair and will have to work your way back through the crazy world of Ivan to set yourself free! This immersive escape room is guaranteed to bring the fun. All of our rooms are private bookings. Reserving this room for a specified time slot guarantees that you will only share the room with YOUR friends and family. One, two Ivan’s coming for you…
